countDownClock-invalidtime: Warning message when pass invalid endTime parameter in {{#countDownClock:endTime}}
countDownClock-days: Days string which will see in Count down time
countDownClock-hours: Hours string which will see in Count down time
countDownClock-minutes: Minutes string which will see in Count down time
countDownClock-seconds: Seconds string which will see in Count down time
countDownClock-expired: Message when count down time has expired
